<figureCitation id="32C5C49CFFB2856A232317D7F0133DE0" box="[517,600,2013,2038]" captionStart="FIGURES 10 – 14" captionStartId="4.[151,264,1818,1840]" captionTargetBox="[176,1414,214,1780]" captionTargetId="figure@4.[158,1428,193,1797]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURES 10 – 14. Figs 10 – 12: Female holotype of Metadon persicus sp. nov. Fig. 10: wing. Fig. 11: frons. Fig. 12: mesoscutum. Figs 13 – 14: Female Metadon nr. persicus. Fig. 13: frons. Fig. 14: mesoscutum. All scale bars = 0.5 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/237595/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="113">
