<number id="1C36CA3EFFB2856A23FA17D4F0B43DE0" box="[732,767,2014,2038]" pageId="1" pageNumber="113" value="1.4">1.4</number>
times as long as wide, abdominal tergites 
<number id="1C36CA3EFFB2856A25FA17D7F74D3DE0" box="[1244,1286,2013,2038]" pageId="1" pageNumber="113" value="4.0" valueMax="5.0" valueMin="3.0">3–5</number>
each with an anterior fascia of golden pile which clearly narrows medially on tergites 
<number id="1C36CA3EFFB1856922FF109DF6493AA6" box="[985,1026,151,176]" pageId="2" pageNumber="114" value="4.5" valueMax="5.0" valueMin="4.0">4–5</number>
